  "keyFeatures": [
    "Guided Omarchy-inspired TUI installer with disk partitioning and config validation",
    "22 desktop environments and window managers selectable at install time",
    "ANIX v1 profile manager for NixOS profiles, snapshots, rollback, and rebuilds",
    "TinyPM v4 app/package layer with Flatpak, Nix, and Snap support",
    "Abora command layer for health checks, recovery, config, and desktop switching",
    "Reproducible ISO builds via Nix flakes",
    "Limine bootloader with Abora branding and Plymouth splash theme",
    "Curated app bundles: Fan Favorites, Essentials, Social, Creator, Developer, Gaming",
    "53-app catalog across 6 categories with declarative NixOS package management",
    "Stable and unstable update channels with one-command updates and rollback"
  ],
